import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"python---intermediate-data-science"}}>{`Python - Intermediate Data Science`}</MDXTag>
{/* TOC -->autoauto- [Python - Intermediate Data Science](#python---intermediate-data-science)auto    - [PYINT-1: Matplotlib](#pyint-1-matplotlib)auto        - [---- PYINT-1.1: Basic plots](#-----pyint-11-basic-plots)autoauto<!-- /TOC */}
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"pyint-1-matplotlib"}}>{`PYINT-1: Matplotlib`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"-----pyint-11-basic-plots"}}>{`---- PYINT-1.1: Basic plots`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Using `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`pyplot`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-python"}}>{`# import pyplot
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

year = [1950, 1970, 1990, 2010]
pop = [2.519, 3.692, 5.263, 6.972]

# make a plot
plt.plot(year, pop)

# show a plot
plt.show()
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`How do we create a scatter plot?`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-python"}}>{`# import pyplot
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

year = [1950, 1970, 1990, 2010]
pop = [2.519, 3.692, 5.263, 6.972]

# make a plot
plt.scatter(year, pop)

# show a plot
plt.show()
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`The basic ingredients of pyplot`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.plot(x,y)
plt.show()
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`You can use certain commands to show a different scale`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`plt.xscale('log')
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
